{"tid":1983351,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 個電腦嗶嗶聲入唔翻","createTime":"2020-04-21T18:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T04:25:45.000Z","uid":121125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1db8ca3998a43feb3d9f694717636967bf254a3e","tid":1983351,"uid":121125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:43:20.000Z","msg":"個電腦都好舊下 不過一直都沒問題<br />\n本來部機都有8GB（有兩條4GB RAM係到），純粹近排諗住加多D RAM用，買多左條4GB RAM用，點知佢話&quot;the following channel did not pass by cpu ram&quot;....之類既野 然後咪諗住restart再插過條ram 點知就開始入唔翻 即使唔用新個條都開唔翻部機<br />\n<br />\n禁開機會開一兩秒就熄左再開過 然後就嗶三下聲，另一個情況就係如果張本身D ram卡插去slot 2 &amp; 4 就會嗶四下聲，完全黑mon沒畫面<br />\n<br />\n試過清塵，刷下RAM條金色邊都唔得<br />\n請問有沒人知係咩事 thanks 唔該大家  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncpu: i5-4460<br />\nram: kingston 4GB x2 新買左條都係4GB<br />\nmotherboard: asrock b85m pro4<br />\ndisplay card: 750ti"},{"pid":"4373b4040e84fb77b21821f29aef7e34a86deb86","tid":1983351,"uid":171513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:51:56.000Z","msg":"都係RAM問題 check cpu針腳 拆電清cmos"},{"pid":"ee34b25849acd8fce76fe30b6168852c744d1d62","tid":1983351,"uid":121125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4373b4040e84fb77b21821f29aef7e34a86deb86","tid":1983351,"uid":171513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:51:56.000Z","msg":"都係RAM問題 check cpu針腳 拆電清cmos"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T21:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔該ching <br />\n會試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係點解突然入唔翻？ 純粹插多左條ram 點解會拔走翻都會連本身部機都開唔翻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ab6bc7e56db46db1ad8cc0c8b92d5b30f0fff8","tid":1983351,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":